data.description: This stunning 3 bed, 2.5 bath townhome, with a two car attached garage is move-in ready, built in 2020 and in the up and coming Painted Prairie neighborhood. Easy access to Denver International Airport, Downtown, and Buckley AFB/SFB. The welcoming open concept leads directly in to the kitchen with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. The primary bedroom, provides a beautiful ensuite bathroom, with double vanity sinks and a walk in closet. Laundry room upstairs provides convenience, along with a tankless water heater. Full bath and secondary rooms complete the upstairs. All appliances/systems are from the 2020 build and will be staying with the home. Painted Prairie Neighborhood regularly host events for the community. Don't wait for the opportunity to call this place home.
